{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_528754914eef4c9db3ebe737","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Feature: Fix Chat Message Display and Add Need Help\n2\t\n3\t## Overview\n4\t\n5\tFix chat message display issue and add help tooltips for each need status.\n6\t\n7\t## Requirements\n8\t\n9\t### 1. Chat Message Display Fix\n10\t**Current Issue**: When user sends a message in chat, the message is not immediately displayed. It only appears after the conversation ends.\n11\t\n12\t**Expected Behavior**:\n13\t- When user clicks \"Send\" button:\n14\t  1. Clear the input box immediately\n15\t  2. Display the user's message in the chat panel immediately\n16\t  3. Show loading state while AI is responding\n17\t  4. Display AI's response when ready\n18\t\n19\t### 2. Need Help Tooltips\n20\tEach need status should have a \"?\" icon that shows a help modal with:\n21\t- Why this need decreases\n22\t- What actions increase this need\n23\t\n24\t**Needs to add help for**:\n25\t- **Happiness (❤️)**: Why decreases (neglect, loneliness) + How to increase (petting, playing)\n26\t- **Hunger (🍗)**: Why decreases (time passes) + How to increase (feeding)\n27\t- **Health (❤️)**: Why decreases (poor care, illness) + How to increase (proper care, medicine)\n28\t- **Energy (⚡)**: Why decreases (activity, lack of sleep) + How to increase (rest, sleep)\n29\t- **Sleep (💤)**: Why decreases (activity, lack of rest) + How to increase (put to bed, rest)\n30\t- **Play (⚽)**: Why decreases (no playtime) + How to increase (play games, toys)\n31\t- **Love (💖)**: Why decreases (neglect, lack of affection) + How to increase (petting, affection)\n32\t- **Chat (💬)**: Why decreases (no conversation) + How to increase (talk to pet)\n33\t- **Knowledge (📚)**: Why decreases (no learning) + How to increase (learn topics, read)\n34\t\n35\t## Acceptance Criteria\n36\t\n37\t- [ ] User message appears immediately after clicking \"Send\"\n38\t- [ ] Input box clears immediately after clicking \"Send\"\n39\t- [ ] Loading indicator shows while AI is responding\n40\t- [ ] Each need has a \"?\" help icon\n41\t- [ ] Clicking \"?\" shows modal with help content\n42\t- [ ] Help content explains why need decreases and how to increase it\n43\t\n44\t## Files to Modify\n45\t\n46\t| File | Change |\n47\t|------|--------|\n48\t| `src/components/Chat.vue` | Fix message display logic, add help tooltips for each need |\n49\t| `src/components/NeedHelpModal.vue` | New component for displaying need help content |\n50\t\n51\t## Technical Approach\n52\t\n53\t1. **Chat Fix**: Modify `sendMessage()` to add user message to chat history immediately before calling AI\n54\t2. **Need Help**: Add \"?\" icon to each need item, create `NeedHelpModal` component with help content\n55\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2d2c4cf8-3212-4753-a963-bc50bd1ec110","uuid":"3ab45d92-f726-478d-a385-951e73fcd4ca","timestamp":"2026-04-10T13:31:48.566Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/home/aixz/data/hxf/bigmodel/ai_code/trellis-worktrees/feature/fix-chat-and-add-need-help/.trellis/tasks/04-10-fix-chat-and-add-need-help/prd.md","content":"# Feature: Fix Chat Message Display and Add Need Help\n\n## Overview\n\nFix chat message display issue and add help tooltips for each need status.\n\n## Requirements\n\n### 1. Chat Message Display Fix\n**Current Issue**: When user sends a message in chat, the message is not immediately displayed. It only appears after the conversation ends.\n\n**Expected Behavior**:\n- When user clicks \"Send\" button:\n  1. Clear the input box immediately\n  2. Display the user's message in the chat panel immediately\n  3. Show loading state while AI is responding\n  4. Display AI's response when ready\n\n### 2. Need Help Tooltips\nEach need status should have a \"?\" icon that shows a help modal with:\n- Why this need decreases\n- What actions increase this need\n\n**Needs to add help for**:\n- **Happiness (❤️)**: Why decreases (neglect, loneliness) + How to increase (petting, playing)\n- **Hunger (🍗)**: Why decreases (time passes) + How to increase (feeding)\n- **Health (❤️)**: Why decreases (poor care, illness) + How to increase (proper care, medicine)\n- **Energy (⚡)**: Why decreases (activity, lack of sleep) + How to increase (rest, sleep)\n- **Sleep (💤)**: Why decreases (activity, lack of rest) + How to increase (put to bed, rest)\n- **Play (⚽)**: Why decreases (no playtime) + How to increase (play games, toys)\n- **Love (💖)**: Why decreases (neglect, lack of affection) + How to increase (petting, affection)\n- **Chat (💬)**: Why decreases (no conversation) + How to increase (talk to pet)\n- **Knowledge (📚)**: Why decreases (no learning) + How to increase (learn topics, read)\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] User message appears immediately after clicking \"Send\"\n- [ ] Input box clears immediately after clicking \"Send\"\n- [ ] Loading indicator shows while AI is responding\n- [ ] Each need has a \"?\" help icon\n- [ ] Clicking \"?\" shows modal with help content\n- [ ] Help content explains why need decreases and how to increase it\n\n## Files to Modify\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `src/components/Chat.vue` | Fix message display logic, add help tooltips for each need |\n| `src/components/NeedHelpModal.vue` | New component for displaying need help content |\n\n## Technical Approach\n\n1. **Chat Fix**: Modify `sendMessage()` to add user message to chat history immediately before calling AI\n2. **Need Help**: Add \"?\" icon to each need item, create `NeedHelpModal` component with help content\n","numLines":55,"startLine":1,"totalLines":55}}}
